x = 0
y = 1
l = [x, y]
for i in range(1000):
    temp = x + y
    l.append( temp )
    x = y
    y = temp
while True:
    a, b = map(int, raw_input().split())
    if a == 0 and b == 0:
        break
    temp = 0
    for i in l:
        if i > b:
            break
        elif i < a:
            continue
        else:
            temp += 1
    print temp
